{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.1","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:1","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.017.058,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Amiti\u00e9 de Jonathan pour David<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-5: cf. (1 S 19:1-7; 20; 23:16-18. 2 S 1:26.) Pr 18:24.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>David avait achev\u00e9 de parler \u00e0 Sa\u00fcl. Et d\u00e8s lors l\u2019\u00e2me de Jonathan fut attach\u00e9e \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e2me de David, et Jonathan l\u2019aima comme son \u00e2me.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.2","name":"1 Samuel 18:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.17.58","name":"1 Samuel 17:58","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.17.58"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.2","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:2","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Ce m\u00eame jour Sa\u00fcl retint David, et ne le laissa pas retourner dans la maison de son p\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.3","name":"1 Samuel 18:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.1","name":"1 Samuel 18:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.3","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:3","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Jonathan fit alliance avec David, parce qu\u2019il l\u2019aimait comme son \u00e2me.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.4","name":"1 Samuel 18:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.2","name":"1 Samuel 18:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.4","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:4","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Il \u00f4ta le manteau qu\u2019il portait, pour le donner \u00e0 David; et il lui donna ses v\u00eatements, m\u00eame son \u00e9p\u00e9e, son arc et sa ceinture.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.5","name":"1 Samuel 18:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.3","name":"1 Samuel 18:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.5","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:5","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>David allait et r\u00e9ussissait partout o\u00f9 l\u2019envoyait Sa\u00fcl; il fut mis par Sa\u00fcl \u00e0 la t\u00eate des gens de guerre, et il plaisait \u00e0 tout le peuple, m\u00eame aux serviteurs de Sa\u00fcl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.6","name":"1 Samuel 18:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.4","name":"1 Samuel 18:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.6","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:6","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.007,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Chant de triomphe des femmes d\u2019Isra\u00ebl. Haine de Sa\u00fcl contre David<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 6-16: cf. Pr 27:4. (1 S 16:14-23; 19:8-10.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Comme ils revenaient, lors du retour de David apr\u00e8s qu\u2019il eut tu\u00e9 le Philistin, les femmes sortirent de toutes les villes d\u2019Isra\u00ebl au-devant du roi Sa\u00fcl, en chantant et en dansant, au son des tambourins et des triangles, et en poussant des cris de joie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.7","name":"1 Samuel 18:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.5","name":"1 Samuel 18:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.7","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:7","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Les femmes qui chantaient se r\u00e9pondaient les unes aux autres, et disaient:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Sa\u00fcl a frapp\u00e9 ses mille,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et David ses dix mille.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.8","name":"1 Samuel 18:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.6","name":"1 Samuel 18:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.8","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:8","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Sa\u00fcl fut tr\u00e8s irrit\u00e9, et cela lui d\u00e9plut. Il dit: On en donne dix mille \u00e0 David, et c\u2019est \u00e0 moi que l\u2019on donne les mille! Il ne lui manque plus que la royaut\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.9","name":"1 Samuel 18:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.7","name":"1 Samuel 18:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.9","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:9","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Et Sa\u00fcl regarda David d\u2019un mauvais \u0153il, \u00e0 partir de ce jour et dans la suite.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.10","name":"1 Samuel 18:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.8","name":"1 Samuel 18:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.10","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:10","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Le lendemain, le mauvais esprit de Dieu saisit Sa\u00fcl, qui eut des transports au milieu de la maison. David jouait, comme les autres jours, et Sa\u00fcl avait sa lance \u00e0 la main.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.11","name":"1 Samuel 18:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.9","name":"1 Samuel 18:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.11","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:11","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Sa\u00fcl leva sa lance, disant en lui-m\u00eame: Je frapperai David contre la paroi. Mais David se d\u00e9tourna de lui deux fois.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.12","name":"1 Samuel 18:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.10","name":"1 Samuel 18:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.12","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:12","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Sa\u00fcl craignait la pr\u00e9sence de David, parce que l\u2019\u00c9ternel \u00e9tait avec David et s\u2019\u00e9tait retir\u00e9 de lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.13","name":"1 Samuel 18:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.11","name":"1 Samuel 18:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.13","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:13","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Il l\u2019\u00e9loigna de sa personne, et il l\u2019\u00e9tablit chef de mille hommes. David sortait et rentrait \u00e0 la t\u00eate du peuple;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.14","name":"1 Samuel 18:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.12","name":"1 Samuel 18:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.14","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:14","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>il r\u00e9ussissait dans toutes ses entreprises, et l\u2019\u00c9ternel \u00e9tait avec lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.15","name":"1 Samuel 18:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.13","name":"1 Samuel 18:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.15","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:15","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Sa\u00fcl, voyant qu\u2019il r\u00e9ussissait toujours, avait peur de lui;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.16","name":"1 Samuel 18:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.14","name":"1 Samuel 18:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.16","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:16","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>mais tout Isra\u00ebl et Juda aimaient David, parce qu\u2019il sortait et rentrait \u00e0 leur t\u00eate.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.17","name":"1 Samuel 18:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.15","name":"1 Samuel 18:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.17","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:17","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.018,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">David gendre du roi<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 17-30: cf. 1 S 17:25. Pr 26:24-27.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Sa\u00fcl dit \u00e0 David: Voici, je te donnerai pour femme ma fille a\u00een\u00e9e M\u00e9rab; sers-moi seulement avec vaillance, et soutiens les guerres de l\u2019\u00c9ternel. Or Sa\u00fcl se disait: Je ne veux pas mettre la main sur lui, mais que la main des Philistins soit sur lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.18","name":"1 Samuel 18:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.16","name":"1 Samuel 18:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.18","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:18","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>David r\u00e9pondit \u00e0 Sa\u00fcl: Qui suis-je, et qu\u2019est-ce que ma vie, qu\u2019est-ce que la famille de mon p\u00e8re en Isra\u00ebl, pour que je devienne le gendre du roi?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.19","name":"1 Samuel 18:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.17","name":"1 Samuel 18:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.19","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:19","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Lorsque arriva le temps o\u00f9 M\u00e9rab, fille de Sa\u00fcl, devait \u00eatre donn\u00e9e \u00e0 David, elle fut donn\u00e9e pour femme \u00e0 Adriel, de Mehola.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.20","name":"1 Samuel 18:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.18","name":"1 Samuel 18:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.20","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:20","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Mical, fille de Sa\u00fcl, aima David. On en informa Sa\u00fcl, et la chose lui convint.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.21","name":"1 Samuel 18:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.19","name":"1 Samuel 18:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.21","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:21","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Il se disait: Je la lui donnerai, afin qu\u2019elle soit un pi\u00e8ge pour lui, et qu\u2019il tombe sous la main des Philistins. Et Sa\u00fcl dit \u00e0 David pour la seconde fois: Tu vas aujourd\u2019hui devenir mon gendre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.22","name":"1 Samuel 18:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.20","name":"1 Samuel 18:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.22","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:22","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Sa\u00fcl donna cet ordre \u00e0 ses serviteurs: Parlez en confidence \u00e0 David, et dites-lui: Voici, le roi est bien dispos\u00e9 pour toi, et tous ses serviteurs t\u2019aiment; sois maintenant le gendre du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.23","name":"1 Samuel 18:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.21","name":"1 Samuel 18:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.23","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:23","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Les serviteurs de Sa\u00fcl r\u00e9p\u00e9t\u00e8rent ces paroles aux oreilles de David. Et David r\u00e9pondit: Croyez-vous qu\u2019il soit facile de devenir le gendre du roi? Moi, je suis un homme pauvre et de peu d\u2019importance.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.24","name":"1 Samuel 18:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.22","name":"1 Samuel 18:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.24","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:24","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Les serviteurs de Sa\u00fcl lui rapport\u00e8rent ce qu\u2019avait r\u00e9pondu David.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.25","name":"1 Samuel 18:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.23","name":"1 Samuel 18:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.25","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:25","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Sa\u00fcl dit: Vous parlerez ainsi \u00e0 David: Le roi ne demande point de dot; mais il d\u00e9sire cent pr\u00e9puces de Philistins, pour \u00eatre veng\u00e9 de ses ennemis. Sa\u00fcl avait le dessein de faire tomber David entre les mains des Philistins.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.26","name":"1 Samuel 18:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.24","name":"1 Samuel 18:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.26","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:26","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Les serviteurs de Sa\u00fcl rapport\u00e8rent ces paroles \u00e0 David, et David agr\u00e9a ce qui lui \u00e9tait demand\u00e9 pour qu\u2019il dev\u00eent gendre du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.27","name":"1 Samuel 18:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.25","name":"1 Samuel 18:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.27","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:27","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Avant le terme fix\u00e9, David se leva, partit avec ses gens, et tua deux cents hommes parmi les Philistins; il apporta leurs pr\u00e9puces, et en livra au roi le nombre complet, afin de devenir gendre du roi. Alors Sa\u00fcl lui donna pour femme Mical, sa fille.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.28","name":"1 Samuel 18:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.26","name":"1 Samuel 18:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.28","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:28","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Sa\u00fcl vit et comprit que l\u2019\u00c9ternel \u00e9tait avec David; et Mical, sa fille, aimait David.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.29","name":"1 Samuel 18:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.27","name":"1 Samuel 18:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.29","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:29","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.018.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Sa\u00fcl craignit de plus en plus David, et il fut toute sa vie son ennemi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.30","name":"1 Samuel 18:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.28","name":"1 Samuel 18:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.30","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 18:30","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.018.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.019.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.18.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Les princes des Philistins faisaient des excursions; et chaque fois qu\u2019ils sortaient, David avait plus de succ\u00e8s que tous les serviteurs de Sa\u00fcl, et son nom devint tr\u00e8s c\u00e9l\u00e8bre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18","name":"1 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.19.1","name":"1 Samuel 19:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.19.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.18.29","name":"1 Samuel 18:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.18.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb2461ff1.89252591');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb2461ff1.89252591\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb2461ff1.89252591","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb2461ff1.89252591'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb2461ff1.89252591\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}